column1: Healthy life expectancy (HLE) at birth and age 65 by sex and upper tier local authorities (UTLAs), England, between 2009 to 2011 and 2014 to 2016
Figures are not available for City of London and Isles of Scilly due to small numbers of deaths and populations.
Excludes residents of communal establishments except NHS housing and students in halls of residence where inclusion takes place at their parents' address.
Healthy life expectancy estimates are based on Upper Tier Local Authorities (UTLAs) in England.
